{"tid":1448682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"算啦不如大家返屋企訓教啦","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:32.000Z","uid":70364,"like":32,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd3626c280603d358f95631fa18865c588c7827","tid":1448682,"uid":70364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"我訓你老母個教呀 成場運動到依家<br />\n比人打撚到咁就叫停哂勇武<br />\n知唔知我地輸既係咩<br />\n我地輸既係唔夠絕 唔夠狼<br />\n由呢一刻開始 真勇武 所有企前排要開始打狗<br />\n唔撚係人地一沖你就散呀屌你老母<br />\n唔撚係手足落單就當人condom呀屌你老母<br />\n要黎一齊黎 要走一齊走 要拉一齊比人拉<br />\n佢既然唔敢成立獨立調查<br />\n就由我地幫佢去調查<br />\n只要一齊沖 一齊攻 我地有人數優勢 一定唔會輸"},{"pid":"54a3c4ee2e5a93ce1febe63ded6f0ede45411cdd","tid":1448682,"uid":259368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"警察還眼！！！"},{"pid":"3735b5584e5fac699f318dc5114527ec7aea4be3","tid":1448682,"uid":224058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:21.000Z","msg":"訓教？<br />\n點訓得著<br />\n宜家仲與5撚過火屎"},{"pid":"da25e441d444ed1d67ed8dfb87dbcdec78535252","tid":1448682,"uid":137887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea70821f26645eb86c38c281d3fd27a361d663b9","tid":1448682,"uid":70364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:07.000Z","msg":"班狗覺得可以打到我地驚 拉到我地驚<br />\n我地要話比佢地知 佢地係錯既"},{"pid":"adbd31b0d66b906ec9ad222e79bf00a4cce73de6","tid":1448682,"uid":79571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:30.000Z","msg":"sor, 睇標題嬲得濟比錯負皮"},{"pid":"9ac910a135865ed97ccddad7fbc186385c8f5cff","tid":1448682,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:52.000Z","msg":"請所有勇武睇睇<br />\n<br />\n我宣布勇武正式退場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447822</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2643eced790bd64d40726e7e2fcf67a829850755","tid":1448682,"uid":70364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:12.000Z","msg":"只要所有人一齊沖 唔會有人會落單<br />\n即使我地前線有鬼都唔撚會驚<br />\n因為一有鬼會比我地打到仆街"},{"pid":"84c3a810ed6e9c6686c1033929c22d6122436362","tid":1448682,"uid":70364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"成個叫勇武退落黎根本就係局<br />\n退左咪冇人搞搞陣囉 <br />\n退左咪大家安安定定去返工囉屌你老母"},{"pid":"8309661ccc308ce09765c59b1984a724e08cf9e6","tid":1448682,"uid":70364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"人地對家一出招你就叫勇武收皮<br />\n比人拉左既手足點算呀<br />\n冇左隻眼既手足點算呀"},{"pid":"2272f05c57662b854e2afa267ea5708a1ab09a86","tid":1448682,"uid":70364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:44:50.000Z","msg":"我唔撚話係文宣冇用呀<br />\n但係班高官最驚係咩？<br />\n係驚成個香港亂呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"aa30646ddcbb788d1a45b3b211e21ca5517985c7","tid":1448682,"uid":70364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:45:37.000Z","msg":"咁多個月和理非 就連一連3日機場集會<br />\n人地政府仲有冇理你班撚樣呀 醒下啦好冇"},{"pid":"e1f6b234ea0f429f8d6bc04ca68a5a3a19593c3e","tid":1448682,"uid":70364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:46:52.000Z","msg":"好老實咁講 你地可以慢慢叫勇武收皮<br />\n叫和理非出黎<br />\n但係作用有幾大<br />\n你同我都心照"},{"pid":"7ddc71f97519553cbc5d132c949d5fbba10af96d","tid":1448682,"uid":70364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:47:40.000Z","msg":"如果大家仲係咁和善<br />\n不如你帶埋你老母真係返屋企訓教啦<br />\n唔好再企出黎啦"},{"pid":"5d5c3d01994f0723721f270f7d16eb49189906c1","tid":1448682,"uid":70364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:48:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要沖一齊沖 一個手足都唔可以少</span></span>"},{"pid":"b60694232ac9a2e5699c762b70d3df9a6fc1068c","tid":1448682,"uid":70364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:48:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要沖一齊沖 一個手足都唔可以少</span></span>"},{"pid":"0bffbbacd927dd1fc167c7853f723876ad14c509","tid"